item.title: Unlimited Colors
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Make your website colorfull and unique!

This theme comes with lots of colors settings, to give you full control over your website colors!



Post format preset colors

You can easily set any color you wish for each of your posts or set colors globaly for post format. So i.e. you can set yellow color for "image" post format and all image posts will be created in yellow.


You can set custom color for each post!

This theme comes with one awesome option to make your posts looks unique and your website colorful & friendly it is unique custom color for each post.

item.title: Post Formats
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Make your website colorfull and unique!


[qd_list]
  • This theme comes with lots of various post formats to completely fulfill your needs. You can show video, images, audio, slideshow or twitter directly at blog listing (9 post formats in total).
  • Each post can have normal or small size, what helps you to adjust its significance.
  • You can also protect your post by password.

  • But what is important, this theme comes with one awesome option to make your posts looks unique and your website colorful and friendly it is unique custom color for each post. You can easily set any color you wish for each of your posts or set colors globaly for post format. So i.e. you can set yellow color for "image" post format and all image posts will be created in yellow.
[/qd_list]

It allows you to change theme look without editing core theme files. And what is important, CSS rules are stored in database and will be saved after theme update.



So you wont loose your changes after update if you use Custom Styles option!

item.title: Translation Ready
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
You can easily translate it to any language

This theme is ready to be translated in other languages than English. It include a .POT file, from which can be easily created .po/.mo files in the language you need.


 

Make it multilingual with WPML

WPLM makes it easy to run a multilingual website with a single WordPress install. Choose languages for your site and start translating content. You can arrange different language contents in the same domain (in language directories), in sub-domains or in completely different domains.
